#### Step 1.2: Validate Story File Exists

**Check if story file exists:**
```
Glob(pattern="devforgeai/specs/Stories/${STORY_ID}*.story.md")

IF no matches found:
    Display: "❌ ERROR: Story file not found"
    Display: ""
    Display: "Looking for: devforgeai/specs/Stories/${STORY_ID}*.story.md"
    Display: ""
    Display: "Available stories:"

    # List all stories
    Glob(pattern="devforgeai/specs/Stories/*.story.md")
    Display: "{list each found story}"

    Display: ""
    Display: "To create this story:"
    Display: "  /create-story [description]"

    HALT execution
    Exit command

ELIF multiple matches found:
    Display: "⚠️ WARNING: Multiple files match '${STORY_ID}'"
    Display: ""
    Display: "Matches found:"
    FOR each matched_file in matches:
        Display: "  - {matched_file}"

    Display: ""
    Display: "Using first match: {matches[0]}"
    Display: ""

    STORY_FILE = matches[0]

ELSE:
    # Single match (expected case)
    STORY_FILE = matches[0]
    Display: "✓ Story file loaded: {STORY_FILE}"
```

