### Phase 3: Verify Completion

**After skill completes, verify results:**

#### Step 3.1: Check Story Status Updated

```
Read(file_path="{STORY_FILE}")

# Extract status from YAML frontmatter
Look for:
  status: [new-status]

IF status == "Dev Complete":
    DEVELOPMENT_SUCCEEDED = true
    Display: ""
    Display: "✅ Development workflow completed successfully"
    Display: ""

ELIF status == "In Development":
    # Skill may have halted due to blocking issue
    DEVELOPMENT_INCOMPLETE = true
    Display: ""
    Display: "⚠️ Development workflow incomplete"
    Display: ""
    Display: "Story status: In Development (not yet complete)"
    Display: "Review skill output above for details on why development halted."

ELSE:
    # Unexpected status
    DEVELOPMENT_FAILED = true
    Display: ""
    Display: "❌ Development workflow may have failed"
    Display: ""
    Display: "Story status: {status} (expected 'Dev Complete')"
    Display: "Review skill output above for errors."
```

